verbs.description: The U.S. Environmental Protection Agency [V: was] ordered by a judge in New York to act on plans to limit the ozone pollution from five states upwind of New York and Connecticut , delivering a legal victory in efforts to force the administration of President Donald Trump to enforce environmental regulations .
